.modal
  .modal-header
    %button.close.dismiss-modal√ó
    %h2 Formatting help
  .modal-body
    %strong Headers
    %pre
      :preserve
        # This is a top-level header
        ## This is an second-level header
        ##### This is a fifth-level header
    %strong Text styles
    %pre
      :preserve
        *This text will be italic*
        _This will also be italic_

        **This text will be bold**
        __This will also be bold__

        *You **can** combine them*
    %strong Unordered
    %pre
      :preserve
        * Item 1
        * Item 2
    %strong Ordered
    %pre
      :preserve
        1. Item 1
        2. Item 2
        3. Item 3
    %strong Images
    %p
      To embed an image in a comment, first it needs to be hosted somewhere (<a href="http://imgur.com">imgur.com</a> is a good option), then you can include it like so:
    %pre
      :preserve
        ![](http://path.to/image.jpg)
    %strong Links
    %pre
      :preserve
        To download a PDF version of the recipe,
        [click here](https://example.com/scrambled-eggs.pdf).
    %strong Blockquotes
    %pre
      :preserve
        As my good friend said:

        > I agree with what everyone
        > has to say.

  .modal-footer
    = link_to t(:close), "#", class: "btn btn-small btn-grey dismiss-modal"

:javascript
  $('.dismiss-modal').click(function(){$('.modal').remove(); return false;})